des:
Currently the Lokha Sabha election 2019 answers about election date of all the constituencies of India. We we have updated the details of who is the candidate in <constiuency> from different parties. Also there would be update of result on election day. 
One can ask 
Ask Lok Sabha, when is election in Udupi?
Tell me election date in Bangalore?
When is MP election in Bellary?
When is election in Shimla?
Who are the candidates in Hyderabad?
Agra candidate please
Tell me candidates name of Shimla
Who are candidates in Agra?
Who is contesting from Wayanad?

Now one can ask 
which ID proofs are valid?
What are the proofs needed for voting?
Kindly revert back with feedback so that we grow. Don't forget to Vote this time.
